zim-tools 1.0.0
===============

 * Remove warnings.
 * Compile zim-tools with travis.
 * Add zim-check tool.
 * Addapt zimDiff and zimPatch to new version of libzim writer.
 * [zimSplit] Do not create a new ofstream for each part. (Do not need gcc5)
